comments.text:
I could NOT live without music. Hell, i cant even go half of a day without me accidentally singing bout random things (like Linda from bobs burgers does). Especially if something makes me super excited; even more so, if i get upset bout anything, then ill just start singing bout it. 😅

Edit: not to even mention that i have tourettes and that i stem alot as well, and both of those cause me to either start singing a line of a song that i know or cause me to make sounds that are musical most of the time. 
(Examples: making beats/simple beatboxing, making "humming" like sounds and singing random gibberish words as if im trying to do instrumental music with my mouth/voice, doing these things together/combo of them...n just other similar shii like this)
